{"tid":1353550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動升級] 嘅然政府仲係唔回應訴求，我地一於搞大佢，一定要有人死方可破局！！","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:07:46.000Z","uid":61161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19c8b0289eb999d875e0aa3e9600fa1f6e5a2fb4","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"暴政已經逼到多名年輕人輕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但林鄭政府一滴眼淚都無輕生者流過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度講多次，你係唔值得為個政權而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能再少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地要一齊見證勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[拋磚] 有無熟讀法律嘅手足？如果逼到人自殺死亡，會唔會有法律責任？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[引玉] 參考：法國黃背心示威已令到今年死咗37個警察，已經超越去年全年數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有第一個深藍絲/警察/政府高層，因為林鄭政府呢個暴政而死，有第二個，第三個嘅時候，你估林鄭政府仲會唔會咁冷血唔回應社會嘅訴求？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0415508cd111487f1a2c2b27bf49c6f6d6e00bad","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a544732c255a98fb03ed8213008d6b732a5f6872","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d3c9bafce12f63356eccc08f290cf05b3248f9","tid":1353550,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"死林鄭都無用， 中共視人命如草介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢親人又唔同， 唔講太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405aec175b115ff29ca707eb713065862744d2dc","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03d3c9bafce12f63356eccc08f290cf05b3248f9","tid":1353550,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"死林鄭都無用， 中共視人命如草介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢親人又唔同， 唔講太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"親政府/黑警死 佢地會唔會有感覺多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba3084572b5085d668499a7baf20ece01c9c712","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"係咪唔work?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e85eb250d2cbd983b8dfbe5fa2fb35cb1c16a4","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"升級"},{"pid":"b8f87f809fadcd538a834d0b411570113efb66ca","tid":1353550,"uid":284779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭一定會安慰藍絲警察，最後受損係手足。"},{"pid":"0dad19864766456a199e9f89b4096dc88a32d7b4","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f87f809fadcd538a834d0b411570113efb66ca","tid":1353550,"uid":284779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭一定會安慰藍絲警察，最後受損係手足。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"點解一定係啲後生死而唔係老野死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad6febf32d94a0b7956390c30e88f8aca0fbac6","tid":1353550,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心示威　仇警氣氛下警員工作壓力增<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=345911&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345911%26refer%3DShare&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUiubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b4d5b091\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345911%26refer%3DShare&h=75a89413\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=345911&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n今年頭三個月，全國已有28名警員輕生，比去年同期多一倍，差不多每四天就有一名警員自殺身亡，頻率是歷來最高。<br />\n<br />\n自殺背後的原因複雜，但普遍認為同警方工作壓力越來越大有關。近年法國恐怖襲擊頻生，警隊工作量急增，加上大批難民湧入，衍生不少執法問題，社會上充斥仇警氣氛，令前線警員壓力更大。"}]}